---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Terms & Conditions: JetAvenue" description="JetAvenue terms and conditions for aircraft maintenance services.">
  <div class="legal-page">
    <h1>Terms & Conditions</h1>
    <p class="last-updated">Last updated: June 2026</p>

    <h2>Acceptance of Terms</h2>
    <p>By accessing this website or engaging JetAvenue for aircraft maintenance services, you agree to be bound by these Terms and Conditions. If you do not agree, please do not use our services.</p>

    <h2>Services</h2>
    <p>JetAvenue provides mobile aircraft maintenance, interior repair, avionics support, and cleaning services. All work is performed by FAA-certified technicians. Scope of work, pricing, and scheduling are confirmed prior to commencement of any service.</p>

    <h2>Estimates & Pricing</h2>
    <p>Any estimates provided are based on the information available at the time of assessment. Final pricing may vary based on actual conditions discovered during service. We will communicate any changes before proceeding with additional work.</p>

    <h2>Limitation of Liability</h2>
    <p>JetAvenue shall not be liable for indirect, incidental, or consequential damages arising from the use of our services. Our liability is limited to the value of the services rendered under the applicable work order.</p>

    <h2>Aircraft Owner Responsibilities</h2>
    <p>The aircraft owner or authorized representative is responsible for ensuring accurate aircraft records are provided, that the aircraft is accessible for service, and that all required approvals and permissions are obtained prior to work commencing.</p>

    <h2>Intellectual Property</h2>
    <p>All content on this website, including text, graphics, and logos, is the property of JetAvenue and may not be reproduced without written permission.</p>

    <h2>Governing Law</h2>
    <p>These Terms are governed by the laws of the State of California. Any disputes shall be resolved in the appropriate courts of Los Angeles County, California.</p>

    <h2>Changes to Terms</h2>
    <p>We reserve the right to update these Terms at any time. Updated terms will be posted on this page with a revised date. Continued use of our services after changes constitutes acceptance.</p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>Questions about these Terms may be directed to <a href="mailto:mx@jetavenue.net">mx@jetavenue.net</a> or by calling <a href="tel:8004805387">800-480-JETS</a>.</p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .legal-page {
    max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto;
    padding: var(--space-xl) var(--space-md);
  }
  .legal-page h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 42px);
    font-weight: 800; color: var(--color-ink); margin: 0 0 8px;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }
  .last-updated {
    font-size: 13px; color: var(--color-body); margin: 0 0 var(--space-lg);
  }
  .legal-page h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-ink); margin: var(--space-lg) 0 8px;
  }
  .legal-page p {
    font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 15px; color: var(--color-body);
    line-height: 1.7; margin: 0;
  }
  .legal-page a { color: var(--color-brand); text-decoration: none; }
  .legal-page a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
</style>
